Among the Innocent: A Stricken Tale will release on Steam on 14 February. Among the Innocent is a first-person adventure thriller set on a remote farm in the Free State in the year 2001. The game is inspired by point-and-click adventure games of the 1990s, with the player taking on the role of struggling writer Peter York. York is trapped in the area and needs explore and solve many mysteries to escape. Developer Zero Degrees said Among the Innocent is the first of five games which form The Stricken Tales – a narrative across multiple decades, characters, and stories. 